#A program that uses a while loop and continuously asks the user to enter a word unless the user enters "chupacabra" as the secret exit word, in which case the message "You've successfully left the loop." should be printed to the screen, and the loop should terminate

secret_word="chupacabra"
while True:
    word = input("Guess a word: ")
    if word == "chupacabra":
        break
print("You've successfully left the loop")

